{"tid":920763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳馬拉松選手集體走捷徑、冒名、套牌代跑","createTime":"2018-11-29T05:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T06:58:42.000Z","uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee5ac171db0c0c26265f5fe3af725a716c2582c","tid":920763,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:12:07.000Z","msg":"【內地馬拉松又出事！】<br />\n【選手集體走捷徑　冒名、套牌代跑】<br />\n<br />\n深圳南山周日舉行了一場半馬拉松，有選手被發現集體走捷徑。馬拉松由華潤大廈出發，途經世界之窗、歡樂谷等地標，跑到一半就要在迴旋處掉頭，在馬路另一邊跑到終點。<br />\n<br />\n結果在中途，就有選手被發現穿過兩條馬路中的綠化帶走捷徑。這一幕被天眼拍下，深圳交警放上微博引發討論。結果愈揭愈多醜聞，有選手被發現冒名代跑，同一個號碼牌卻有三個人掛著，其中有兩個人還在一起「跑孖嗶」。<br />\n<br />\n這些片段和相被放上網後，馬拉松主辦方發聲明，批評這些選手破壞了比賽規則和秩序，違反了體育精神，將會核實他們身份，查證後會公布違規名單和處罰結果。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#馬拉松<br />\n#走捷徑<br />\n<br />\n片：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1954533551357788/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1954533551357788%2F&d=mACj9ENjUeoNIvMCPSypFROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=210973c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1954533551357788/</a>"},{"pid":"4a8cd401990196b8c52fdf863388e0de5f049ebb","tid":920763,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"6ad7dad75efaea95ced28b2d5136821453f3f230","tid":920763,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a8cd401990196b8c52fdf863388e0de5f049ebb","tid":920763,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"千術係中國國粹黎"},{"pid":"eecceda15ead5c6267a4fe9b5ccc9c934f804c1b","tid":920763,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"chi na style"},{"pid":"869957c7b72797f0a9920fb6eaa84e6f04f2b0bd","tid":920763,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"中國模式：捉到老鼠就係好貓，體育精神vs 贏，中國人心裡有數"},{"pid":"944eef7f7c7458de1f37c9ac59b408a8d03cf3a9","tid":920763,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"深圳好先進"}]}